    "I look away."
    voice "11-3-18.mp3" #potato
    pro "What about everyone else?"
    voice "11-3-19.mp3" #starleeter
    lov "It’ll be okay."
    "She squeezes my hand."
    voice "11-3-20.mp3" #starleeter
