    voice "11-3-26.mp3" #potato
    pro "‘Everything is going to be okay. I’m going to make it right.’"
    voice "11-3-27.mp3" #starleeter
    lov "See? Everything’s fine!"
    voice "11-3-28.mp3" #potato
